supposedly this is enough for doing two doors

00:00:46.090 --> 00:00:49.800
 although I recommend you go to
their site and take a look at the way

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.960
they recommend doing it first

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.930
uh... I want to do it a little bit
different than their directions to try

00:00:54.930 --> 00:00:59.400
to help simplify the process for the
homeowners and do-it-yourselfers 

